data.title: Christopher Koch
data.text:
Chris has over 30 years of commercial real estate brokerage experience. In addition to representing tenants, he spent a portion of his career specializing in landlord representation, focusing on institutional office property ownership. He has completed transactions in multiple real estate disciplines, including office, medical, flex, warehouse, multi-family, and self-storage. Chris takes particular pride in paying attention to the details of a transaction that others might miss. In his role as Transaction Manager at Keyser, his unique perspective and skill set is an invaluable support resource in achieving successful outcomes for clients.
